# Free Tier Constraints

This project must run entirely on free tiers. See AGENTS.md for full details.

Key rules:
- Backend storage is **ephemeral only** — use `backend/tmp/` (local filesystem), never external object storage.
- No paid services: no S3, Redis, Celery workers, or paid APIs.
- Background cleanup must be in-process (`BackgroundTasks` or `asyncio.create_task`).
- Frontend must produce a **static build** to `frontend/dist/` for GitHub Pages.
- Keep backend memory under ~400 MB to stay within free tier limits.
- Free tier servers sleep — design endpoints to handle cold starts (fast startup, lazy init).
